                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">They also received statements both written and oral, from the
                    Austrian Government, reproduced in the following <gloss target="#t_CFM1">C.F.M.</gloss> documents: <table cols="5" rend="width: 50%" rendition="#center-block" rows="4">
                        <row>
