                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Union of South Africa</cell>
                            <cell>“</cell>
                            <cell>“</cell>
                            <cell>7</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">In every case except that of the second Brazilian communication
                    the observations submitted referred to the question of procedure.</p>
